Anime Ocean City Welcomes Special Guest Edwin Huang! 🎉

@ironpinky Edwin Huang is a California based comic artist, illustrator, and storyboard artist. Edwin is best known for his published work on Street Fighter, Mortal Kombat, Marvel, Mega Man, and Skullkickers.
He has also worked on Archie Comics’, Sonic the Hedgehog comic book series and its spin-offs, as well as Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles.

Tickets on sale now at: 
🦀www.animeoceancity.com 🦀
